What if, work of die was only uptill one gets a six... And that would unlock all 4 gotis, and thereafter, all users can move 1 goti, 1 block, at a time (ie. Instead of it will always be 1, will all other bonus chance accepted)... This will make it like a snake Game... And another special thing will be that, user will have to try to not keep much gotis together since they will just get sweeped away in a single move (kyunki pehle ko markar, bonus me again can move 1, and in this way it can clear all, if 4 gotis are in same place)
Except from the randomness removed (which actually is an important part of it), and that all 4 gotis get activated at once... ALL OTHER RULES SAME
Think about it... Can we unlock 2 gotis at start, and 1 more after each kill by that gotis?
